IBM's Qiskit - Quantum Explorers 2023-2024¶

Badge #3: Eminent Scientist - Quantum Women Invited Talks¶

Table of Contents¶

  • Story

  • Unlock Your Badge

Story¶

As you travel among the stars, you encounter technologies beyond your wildest dreams. You believe you can harness these technologies to enhance your starship. Improving your lab instruments, incorporating novel technology like replication, building a flourishing aeroponics bay for fresh food, holodecks, boosting your weaponry--you name it!

(Share how you would enhance your starship in the #space-exploration channel on Discord!)

Unlock this badge to gain the rank of Eminent Scientist, and level-up your starship from amazing to out of this world.

Instructions¶

The Eminent Scientist badge is a community badge, which means this is associated with a community activity, namely the Quantum Women Invited Talk series.

About the Quantum Women Invited Talk series¶

This series highlights accomplished women in the industry to inspire the next generation of quantum researchers and developers. Tune in to hear about their journey into and within quantum. Things like how they overcame challenges, their career path and achievements, what theyre working on, and their vision for the future of the industry, along with any other inspiration and advice theyd like to share!

Tasks to complete to unlock this achievement¶

  • Eminent Scientist Badge-Kick-off: Quantum Women Invited Talks

    Date: July 24, 2023

    Time: 6:00 PM IST | 8:30 AM EDT View this time in your own timezone here.

    The recording will be available at the link provided.

  • Attend at least one Quantum Women Invited Talk

    The talks will take place occasionally throughout the Quantum Explorers program. Keep an eye on the #announcements channel and the #q-women-invited-talks channel for invited talk announcements. All recordings will be available for those who cannot make it live.

  • Learn from these inspiring women!

    While you are only required to attend one event, we encourage you to attend as many as possible and watch past talk recordings to gain valuable knowledge and inspiration from these remarkable women in the quantum industry.

  • Make a note of the password revealed during the event

    This badge does not have a quiz associated with it. A password will be announced and shared during the event. It will also be available in the closed captions of the video. Important Note: please do not share the password with anyone.

The Eminent Scientist workbook is a downloadable PDF that includes the tasks you must complete, has interactable checkboxes, and note sections. You can use this to track your progress and take notes.

For any questions or discussions about the Eminent Scientist badge, please use the #q-women-invited-talks channel on Discord.
